snippet.title: Funny animals will make you burst into laughter - Funny animal compilation
snippet.description:
Animals make us happy and laugh! They are so adorable, cute and funny! Here's a compilations where you will see a lot of funny beluga whales, raccoons, squirrels, mirror reactions,... What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
